ZH: 我会一直陪着你。
EN: I will always accompany you.

ZH: 他们陪我去逛商店。
EN: They accompany me to go shopping.

ZH: 她会陪你练习钢琴。
EN: She will accompany you to practice the piano.

ZH: 我愿意陪你走到世界的尽头。
EN: I am willing to accompany you to the end of the world.

ZH: 请陪我走一段路。
EN: Please accompany me for a walk.

ZH: 我想找个人陪我看电影。
EN: I want to find someone to accompany me to watch a movie.

ZH: 如果你寂寞了，我会陪你聊天。
EN: If you are lonely, I will accompany you to chat.

ZH: 她很乐意陪孩子玩乐。
EN: She is happy to accompany the children to play.

ZH: 老板有事要我陪他出差。
EN: The boss wants me to accompany him on a business trip.

ZH: 我已经找到一个陪我去旅行的伴侣。
EN: I have found a companion to accompany me on the trip.

ZH: 他答应陪我去看医生。
EN: He promised to accompany me to see the doctor.

ZH: 他陪她参加了一个派对。
EN: He accompanied her to a party.

ZH: 老人在家里独自，我想陪他聊天。
EN: The old man is alone at home, I want to accompany him to chat.

ZH: 他陪她学习英语。
EN: He accompanies her to study English.

ZH: 我们一起陪她度过难关。
EN: We accompany her through the difficult times.

ZH: 请陪我等一下。
EN: Please accompany me for a moment.

ZH: 老公从不陪我去购物。
EN: My husband never accompanies me shopping.

ZH: 她真心地陪伴我一起成长。
EN: She sincerely accompanies me to grow together.

ZH: 我愿意陪你直到明天的日出。
EN: I am willing to accompany you until tomorrow's sunrise.

ZH: 他们互相陪伴，永远不分离。
EN: They accompany each other, never separate.
